quran[9{c,v,t}:
25,12,woh jab daur se inn ko dekhe gi to yeh uss ke ghazab aur josh ki aawazian sun len ge
25,13,aur jab yeh dast o pa basta uss mein aik tang jagah thonse jayen ge to apni mout ko pukarnay lagen ge
25,14,( uss waqt un se kaha jaye ga ke ) aaj aik mout ko nahi bohat si mouton ko poukaro
25,15,"inn se pucho, yeh injaam acha hai ya woh Abdi jannat jis ka wada khuda tars parhaiz garon se kya gaya hai? jo unn ke aamaal ki jaza aur unn ke safar ki aakhri manzil ho gi"
25,16,"jis mein unn ki har khwahish poori ho gi, jis mein woh hamesha hamesha rahen ge, jis ka ataa karna tumahray parvar-digaar ke zimmay aik wajib alada wada hai"
25,17,"aur woh wohi din ho ga jab ke ( tumhara rab ) inn logon ko bhi ghair laaye ga aur un ke unn mabodon ko bhi bُla le ga jinhein aaj yeh Allah ko chore kar پوج rahay hain, phir woh unn se pouchye ga"" kya tum ne mere inn bundon kar gumraah kya tha? ya yeh khud raah e raast se bhatak gay thay? """
25,18,"woh arz karen ge"" pak hai aap ki zaat, hamari to yeh bhi majaal nah thi ke aap ke siwa kisi ko apna maula banayen magar aap ne inn ko aur un ke baap dada ko khoob samanِ zindagi diya hatta ke yeh sabaq bhool gay aur shamat zada ho kar rahay """
25,19,"yun jhutla den ge woh ( tumahray mabood ) tumhari unn baton ko jo aaj tum keh rahay ho, phir tum nah apni shamat taall sakuu ge nah kahin se madad pa sakuu ge aur jo bhi tum mein se zulm kere usay hum sakht azaab ka maza chkhayin ge"
25,20,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay jo rasool bhi hum ne beje hain woh sab bhi khana khanay walay aur baazaaron mein chalne phirnay walay log hi thay darasal hum ne tum logon ko aik dosray ke liye azmaish ka zareya bana diya hai kya tum sabr karte ho? tumhara rab sab kuch daikhta hai"
